    • appendTo

      public void appendTo(ToStringTreeAppender appender)
      Description copied from interface: ToStringTreeAppendable
      Appends information about this to the given appender.

      WARNING: This generally shouldn't be called directly, as ToStringTreeAppender will automatically call this method for ToStringTreeAppendable values passed to ToStringTreeAppender.attribute(String, Object)/ToStringTreeAppender.value(Object).

      Implementations should assume that calls to ToStringTreeAppender.startObject()/ToStringTreeAppender.endObject() for this are handled by the caller.
